# KATRIN-analysis
A package for Bayesian analysis of KATRIN experiment.

This package relies on a specified version of PyStan, which can be downloaded [here](https://github.com/thuxwr/pystan.git@root_supported).

Please follow the instructions [here](https://github.com/thuxwr/Morpho_ROOT_support/blame/master/README.md) to setup the required environment.

ROOT classes used in this package are: TFile, TH1D, TH2D, TGraph, TF1, TMath, TRandom3 and TMinuit. Please make sure to include the according headers in your PyStan.
